overview: Documentary about the student bar at the Université de Moncton in New Brunswick. Witness of the political and social demands of the end of the sixties, then of the cultural explosion which followed, the Kacho is closed since 1996. In this delirious happening composed of sequences of archives and recent shooting, Marie-Jo Thério and the band Les Païens go wild, marry poems and music.
title: Kacho Komplo
